Just thought that I would let everyone know that I have not dissapeared, but will still be working on Rawr.Enhance.  Moving house (and being caught in a flood) has hampered my efforts to get consistant internet access.

Please keep reporting any problems with the module, and I'll put it on my list of things to fix.
As you are from Australia, fingers crossed that your new house isn't in Brisbane and under water.
